# Astro Red - Cyberpunk space theme inspired by astronaut imagery
# Primary accent: Vibrant red/coral from helmet glow
# Dark space background with high contrast
#
# Installation:
#   1. Copy this file to ~/.config/ghostty/themes/astro-red
#   2. Add "theme = astro-red" to your ~/.config/ghostty/config
#   3. Reload config with Cmd+Shift+, (macOS) or Ctrl+Shift+, (Linux)

